	<h1>About Us</h1> 
	<p> 
		Are you too busy to plan dinner?  We are too.  That's why we built RealMealz to quickly discover 30 minute meals using ingredients we already bought.  This way, we eat  real food that is cooked fresh, and the food we bought doesn't go to waste.  Sometimes, the food pictures inspire us to plan ahead a few meals too.  Discover for yourself how RealMealz can help you cook more and eat better.  It certainly helped us and our families do the same.
		
	<br><br>
	<div class="about-us-divider">
  	<b>How are we different from Epicurious and cooks.com?</b>
	</div>
		<ol>
  		<li>We streamline for everyday homecooking. We focus on main-dish recipes made in 30 minutes or less.  No fuss. Just fast, tasty and homemade.  </li>
  		<li>New(-ish) to the kitchen? Don't worry. You don't need to know all the catch phrases and dish names and type them in for a recipe search. We inspire your appetite rather than make you search: you don't have to know what you want.  Tell us what's in your fridge and we'll give you some ideas with some beautiful food photos.   </li>
  		<li>Want a personal kitchen assistant that remembers your diet needs? That's us. We filter according to your preferences.  Tell us what you are avoiding (allergy, ethical or personal reasons are all valid) and you won't see a recipe you can't eat. </li>
		</ol>
<br><div class="about-us-divider"><b>Who are we?</b></div>
	<p>
